// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0781 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: b2596882-97cf-5ef2-b69d-d1fcce805523

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*")
